name: Encore
description:
Use this model and 1000+ more for free on HappyAccidents.AI

From the maker of ICBINP, one last model.

This is a mix of the favourite versions of models I've made (specifics in the 'About This Version' info), which ended up making a silky smooth and yet surprisingly versatile model that I think you'll like!

All sample images made without LoRAs or Embeddings. The man in the suit and the woman in the sundress were made using prompts and settings that should be replicable on any UI (less than 75 token prompt, Euler A, size is multiple of 64, no hires fix, no skipped clip layers etc)

As always, model has had basic prune to fp16 and VAE baked in (840k)

modelVersions.name: Encore
modelVersions.description:
0.5 Mix of Dumb Monkey & Optimus Primate v3, add 0.3 of RCNZ Cartoon 3d v2, add 0.3 of JAFA Mix 5c (unreleased, hiding on Huggingface if you really want it along with a heap of other testing versions), and 0.3 of ICBINP vFinal

Or at least that's what I think I remember.. the order of the merge is correct, the weights might be out!
